name: Brown Leather Mandible Belt
description: These 100% leather belts come packaged in our limited edition packaging, these items were made to be the highest quality possible. The Belt The belt is 100% leather with a continuous embossing all over of our Jaw bone repeat pattern, even through the small details and features a replaceable / removable oxidized metal buckle. The belt is designed to be personal / perfect for you and should be cut to size. The uncut item measures 120cm long. The Packaging The item will come plastic wrapped, tagged and covered in tissue paper to keep the leather fresh in the box. The box is a hand made custom drawer box with ribbon pull featuring our logo silver foil embossed onto the top. Topped off with a leather care leaflet inside.
